title: Spinach and Feta Strudel
ingredients: ['125ml olive oil', '1 bunch spring onions, chopped', '575g frozen chopped spinach, thawed, well drained', '2 tablespoons chopped fresh dill', '3 extra large eggs, lightly beaten', '200g feta cheese, crumbled', '1/4 teaspoon salt', '1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper', '40 sheets filo pastry, thawed if frozen', '225g unsalted butter, melted', '55g plain breadcrumbs']
